    "GPT-4V and Claude-3 both show small positive regression coefficients with humans answers: 0.15 (95% CI 0.09, 0.21) with an R 2 value of 0.025, and 0.17 (95% CI 0.11, 0.23) with an R 2 value of 0.032, respectively.",
    "Again, no model coefficient is close to the human-to-human coefficient of 0.83 (95% CI 0.80, 0.87) with an R 2 value of 0.688.",
